                            also use cookies to help us with geolocation tracking in order to present you with the
                            closest stores and content and click and collect locations. Additionally, cookies allow us
                            to serve you specific content, such products you are interested in, customise your shopping
                            experience. We may employ the learnings of your behaviour on our SplitChek to serve you with
                            targeted advertisements on third-party products in an effort to “re-market” our products and
                            services to you.</p>
                    </div>

